Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.37,0:00:06.72,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Travel across the oceans of the world
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.74,0:00:08.98,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Bellow a battle cry
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.00,0:00:17.00,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Once your heart feels refreshed,\Nlet the signal to set sail ring out
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.09,0:00:26.49,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,We've left the established course
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.51,0:00:30.08,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, we're rowing straight toward
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.10,0:00:35.63,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,The borderline between the sky and the ocean
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.65,0:00:41.76,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,In the dark depths of the ocean,\Nadventure holds its breath
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.78,0:00:48.56,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you have a good time just imagining it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.58,0:00:53.02,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Travel across the oceans of the world
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.04,0:00:55.32,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Bellow a battle cry
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.34,0:01:03.34,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Once your heart feels refreshed,\Nlet the signal to set sail ring out
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.43,0:01:12.83,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"That feeling" I get when embarking
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.85,0:01:16.38,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Is something I hope to remember always
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.40,0:01:21.97,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,If I can, I won't be afraid of anything
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.99,0:01:28.10,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,With our pulses racing, \Nlet's go on a trip now
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.12,0:01:34.85,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Shy hearts engrave the rhythm of adventure
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.87,0:01:39.40,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Snatch up the treasure here and there
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.42,0:01:41.65,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,While laughing out loud
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.67,0:01:45.99,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,As we dash by like a noisy party
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.01,0:01:49.04,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Make some waves...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.06,0:01:50.66,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Life is "Adventurous"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.68,0:01:52.37,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Be aware it's "Dangerous"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.39,0:01:54.08,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's gonna be "One of us"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.10,0:01:55.71,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,And a trip goes on because
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.73,0:01:57.38,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,We da pirate of the "Mass"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.40,0:01:59.05,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,To the West, To the East
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.07,0:02:00.42,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Gotta find my way, Sail away
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.44,0:02:01.51,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,All the way to "One piece"!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.53,0:02:05.89,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Stuff a dream into your empty chest
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.91,0:02:08.18,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,And spread your wings
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.20,0:02:12.52,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,If the wind blowing through\Nthem dyes your heart
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.54,0:02:14.69,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's press forward
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.71,0:02:19.07,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Snatch up the treasure here and there
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.09,0:02:21.40,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,While laughing out loud
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.42,0:02:25.74,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,As we dash by like a noisy party
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.76,0:02:32.82,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Make some waves...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.84,0:02:37.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wealth, fame, power...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.13,0:02:39.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gold Roger, the King of the Pirates,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.89,0:02:42.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,once attained everything\Nthis world has to offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.97,0:02:45.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The words he uttered just before his death
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.31,0:02:49.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,drove people around the world to the seas.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.27,0:02:53.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My treasure? If you want it, you can have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.48,0:02:58.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Find it! I left everything\Nthis world has to offer there!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.36,0:03:03.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so men rushed onto the\NGrand Line in pursuit of romanticism!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.45,0:03:08.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The world has truly entered \Na Great Pirate Era!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.93,0:03:11.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Perona-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.55,0:03:14.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Moria-sama is summoning the Three Phantoms.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.64,0:03:17.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The master beckons? Whatever for?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.27,0:03:20.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've heard that Straw Hat\NLuffy has been captured!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.06,0:03:23.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He wants to make a show\Nout of reanimating No. 900!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.19,0:03:24.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Absalom!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.78,0:03:27.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing here? This is my room.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.74,0:03:30.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome back, Perona-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.95,0:03:34.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zip it, Kumacy! How many times\Nmust I tell you not to talk?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.41,0:03:37.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see you're as harsh on Kumacy as ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.03,0:03:39.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're beary harsh.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.29,0:03:43.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,More importantly, have you heard?\NThe master is summoning us.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.46,0:03:46.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They still haven't found us,\Nif you can believe that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.51,0:03:47.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a miracle!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.72,0:03:51.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did we hide here in the first place?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.72,0:03:53.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We didn't have much choice!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.61,0:03:57.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who knew Beast Man was \Ngonna catch up so soon?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.07,0:03:59.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I didn't realize this was a zombie!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.98,0:04:02.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's look for a chance to make\Na break for it. Sound good?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.31,0:04:04.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Absalom-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.11,0:04:07.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So this is where you went!\NI have something that I'd like to tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.65,0:04:08.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.65,0:04:11.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like we have one more\Nintruder on top of the pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.20,0:04:12.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An intruder?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.82,0:04:15.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the Humming Swordsman!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.20,0:04:20.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.50,0:04:28.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Weapons Left!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.67,0:04:33.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nico Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.85,0:04:39.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They've never failed to catch\Nour prey, not even once!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.35,0:04:46.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We hung out quietly in the ceiling\Nand snatched your friends up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.07,0:04:50.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now we'll take you to the same\Nplace we took your friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.49,0:04:52.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brace yourselves!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.70,0:04:58.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ Yo ho ho ho, yo ho ho ho... ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.24,0:04:58.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is it?! Who's singing that song?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.24,0:05:06.24,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ Yo ho ho ho, yo ho ho ho ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.92,0:05:11.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Goodness, I see everyone really\Ndid disembark onto this island.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.59,0:05:13.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How did you get up here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.68,0:05:15.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I jumped.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.14,0:05:16.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm light!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.68,0:05:20.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seeing as you're here, I suppose\Nyou've left me with no other choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.35,0:05:23.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I shall tell you everything \Nabout this island.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.02,0:05:25.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Who the hell are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.02,0:05:27.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You aren't a zombie, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.07,0:05:29.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I bet you're with these pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.48,0:05:31.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Skeleton!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.28,0:05:35.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, yes. Not to worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.28,0:05:37.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The fight is already over.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.74,0:05:39.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.24,0:05:43.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Three-Pace Hum...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.96,0:05:51.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Notch Slash!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.34,0:05:59.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Luffy's Emergency Situation!\NThe Ultimate Shadow's Destination!"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.11,0:06:12.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The fight's not over!\NSwords don't work on zombies!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.94,0:06:17.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's gonna pop back up!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.70,0:06:20.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Curse you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.70,0:06:22.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a sec...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.55,0:06:27.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've seen you somewhere before!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.17,0:06:30.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not to worry! I've already dealt with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.63,0:06:32.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.84,0:06:40.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even zombies have weaknesses!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.65,0:06:50.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.50,0:06:53.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the zombie's "soul."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.15,0:06:56.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His soul?! But I can see it leaving his body!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.90,0:06:59.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,C-Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.12,0:07:01.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's high time you returned...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.49,0:07:09.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...to your rightful master!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.43,0:07:26.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Tararan!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.68,0:07:30.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain! He took out the captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.02,0:07:32.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.40,0:07:35.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He isn't budging an inch...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.15,0:07:38.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.53,0:07:39.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I purified him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.61,0:07:41.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You what?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.20,0:07:45.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look! He's definitely the\N"Humming Swordsman"!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.37,0:07:49.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Five years ago, he wreaked\Nhavoc on Thriller Bark.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.42,0:07:51.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've gotta tell the master!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.75,0:07:58.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry! Hurry! Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.34,0:08:01.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That spider web is strong\Nagainst physical attacks,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.22,0:08:02.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but weak against fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.76,0:08:07.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.89,0:08:13.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right! It melts right off!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.44,0:08:16.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They got Straw Hat and the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.23,0:08:19.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y'know, you seem mighty\Nknowledgeable about this island...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.65,0:08:23.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am, but I don't know where to begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.70,0:08:29.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If they've been caught, \Nwe're probably too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.54,0:08:32.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! It's too late?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.08,0:08:34.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,P-Please don't yell at me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.92,0:08:39.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It makes me jump under my skin!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.09,0:08:43.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm a skeleton, so I don't have any skin!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.14,0:08:47.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's my skull humor!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.52,0:08:50.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't bother. He's already dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.02,0:08:54.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, please put the\Njoking aside and hear me out.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.90,0:08:57.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't bother! He's already dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.61,0:09:01.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As I already told you,\Nwithout a working rudder,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.65,0:09:06.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I spent decades wandering these seas alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.12,0:09:09.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I wanted to escape \Nfrom the Devil's Sea,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.04,0:09:13.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was at the mercy of the tide\Nbecause of my broken rudder.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.29,0:09:16.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now let's go back to about five years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.96,0:09:23.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Much like you and your crewmates,\NI was "invited" to Thriller Bark.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.05,0:09:26.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Desperate to leave the Florian Triangle,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.18,0:09:28.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I walked around this island in hopes
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.90,0:09:33.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,of finding the parts I \Nneeded to fix my rudder.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.27,0:09:37.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if anything is down here... Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.07,0:09:39.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is that?! Crap! Crap! Crap! Crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.86,0:09:42.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Scary! Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.86,0:09:47.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Freaky! I hate ghosts!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.28,0:09:51.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All I found were monsters and zombies.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.70,0:09:55.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the end, they caught me and\Nbrought me here to this building.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.00,0:09:58.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Inside, I saw...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.84,0:10:02.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...a martial arts dancer who\Nthey caught before me...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.51,0:10:06.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and a type of corpse covered\Nin stitches called a "mario."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.84,0:10:11.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A ghastly giant appeared before them!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.27,0:10:15.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was incredible!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.31,0:10:18.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He peeled the man's shadow off the ground...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.36,0:10:20.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and snip, snip!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.19,0:10:22.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He cut the man's shadow off?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.28,0:10:24.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I questioned my eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.53,0:10:26.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.52,0:10:31.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that I have any eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.34,0:10:33.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're asking for a knuckle sandwich!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.83,0:10:41.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Feel free to let him have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.47,0:10:52.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shortly thereafter, I suffered the same fate.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.35,0:10:55.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The man who lost his shadow\Ncollapsed on the spot.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.89,0:11:01.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His severed shadow was stuffed\Ninto the inanimate mario.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.73,0:11:04.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now what do you think happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.74,0:11:10.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The "mario" corpse got \Nup and started to move!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.28,0:11:12.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How's that work?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.33,0:11:19.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shadows are our "second souls" that are\Nalways with us, moving as we dictate.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.08,0:11:21.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is true of your shadows as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.50,0:11:23.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Normally, these "souls" always stay with you,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.67,0:11:27.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,following your every moment from\Nthe moment you're born until you die.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.80,0:11:32.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is a giant of a man who captures\Nthem and makes them do his bidding!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.93,0:11:37.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He is one of the Seven Warlords\Nof the Sea, Gecko Moria!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.48,0:11:40.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He has eaten the Shadow-Shadow Fruit!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.52,0:11:42.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A Devil Fruit, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.46,0:11:46.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is he the one who stole your shadow?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.69,0:11:50.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A certain man stole my\Nshadow a few years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.96,0:11:52.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your shadow?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.24,0:11:54.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does that sorta thing actually happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.29,0:11:56.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, it does.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.29,0:12:03.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And having lost my shadow, I am no\Nlonger able to exist in the world of light.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.25,0:12:08.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I cannot live under the light of the sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.30,0:12:11.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What would happen if you\Nwere hit by the sunlight?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.64,0:12:17.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I was directly hit by sunlight, my body...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.10,0:12:23.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...would be obliterated!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.48,0:12:29.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as he has a corpse, he can use\Na shadow to turn it into a zombie.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.36,0:12:34.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The real problem is that his cohort\Nis the genius surgeon, Dr. Hogback.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.66,0:12:39.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He can reconstruct the body,\Nmaking it stronger than before!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.41,0:12:42.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sometimes he uses his medical\Nexpertise to revive the flesh
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.00,0:12:46.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,of legendary warriors from around the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.34,0:12:53.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And he has a tremendous collection of mario\Ncurrently preserved in his lab freezer.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.59,0:12:55.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dr. Hogback...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.85,0:12:58.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't realize the renowned\Ndoctor has been here
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.60,0:13:02.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,assisting a pirate ever \Nsince he went missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.52,0:13:06.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So those zombies are reanimated corpses,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.07,0:13:09.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but it's not like he actually\Nrevived the dead, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.49,0:13:11.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Exactly!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.86,0:13:16.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The shadow provides their\Npersonality and fighting abilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.37,0:13:20.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The power of their body depends on\Nthe physical ability of their mario.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.62,0:13:23.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you combine a strong body\Nwith a strong shadow,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.92,0:13:31.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it will create an even stronger zombie!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.34,0:13:36.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is why Moria is eager to get\Nhis hands on wanted men's shadows!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.22,0:13:40.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I getcha! No wonder he came after us.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.06,0:13:42.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's the deal with Thriller Bark.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.60,0:13:48.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Moria's favorite aspect about\Nzombies could be their obedience.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.11,0:13:52.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Generally, it's a challenge to\Nkeep powerful warriors in line.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.65,0:13:58.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, but our shadows possess\Nthe same abilities as us.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.08,0:14:01.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once he has our shadows,\Nhe can toss us troublemakers out.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.75,0:14:06.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The powerful are quickly returned to\Nthe sea while they're still unconscious.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.67,0:14:09.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, they're in trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.01,0:14:11.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't worry yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.94,0:14:13.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We still have time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.93,0:14:17.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will tell you the best way to handle this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.22,0:14:20.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please believe me and do as I instruct.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.68,0:14:24.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! You want us to believe you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.81,0:14:29.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good sir, I'm shocked to the skull!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.86,0:14:37.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, I haven't bickered like\Nthis in decades, so I'm eating it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.28,0:14:43.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll hear you out, so get talking!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.66,0:14:47.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Certainly!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.67,0:14:50.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.17,0:14:53.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Moria-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.97,0:14:56.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Three Phantoms have gathered together!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.80,0:14:59.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was quick! Enter!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.18,0:15:07.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.57,0:15:18.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you're here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.16,0:15:21.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Turn me into the King of the Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.16,0:15:22.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're on it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.91,0:15:27.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't become the King of the Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.62,0:15:30.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The future King of the Pirates...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.25,0:15:38.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...is me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.93,0:15:50.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Untie this rope, you oversized shallot!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.15,0:15:53.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give Usopp, Nami, Chopper,\NSanji, and Zoro back!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.78,0:15:56.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where'd you hide them, shallot head?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.11,0:15:58.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This one has lot of fight in him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.78,0:16:01.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So this is Straw Hat Luffy, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.03,0:16:03.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a hard time believing this is the man
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.49,0:16:06.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,who picked a fight with the World Government.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.54,0:16:10.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is he wearing General Zombie armor?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.04,0:16:14.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you get it? This is every guy's dream!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.21,0:16:18.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You got captured, so don't\Nlecture me about dreams!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.17,0:16:22.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Straw Hat Luffy! You've made\Na pretty big name for yourself,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.72,0:16:26.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but you're only our third catch so far.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.18,0:16:32.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've got Pirate Hunter Zoro and some\Nblond guy who didn't have a wanted poster.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.73,0:16:40.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Sanji's the only blond in my crew...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.32,0:16:44.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Hey, it sounds like\Nthey caught Zoro and Sanji.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.70,0:16:47.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way! And they even have Luffy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.91,0:16:54.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Why did the three monsters\Nhave to be the first to get caught?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.50,0:16:59.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no idea who these guys are,\Nbut they're definitely bad news!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.05,0:17:03.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, what happened\Nto that trio, Perona?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.93,0:17:07.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I recall handing them over\Nto the Risky Brothers.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.10,0:17:09.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Kumacy never got them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.98,0:17:12.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You sure they didn't \Nescape on their way over?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.40,0:17:14.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bingo!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.81,0:17:20.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're talking about us.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.45,0:17:24.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The casket popped open!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.62,0:17:25.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.95,0:17:32.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jerks!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.87,0:17:34.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Usopp! Nami!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.46,0:17:42.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hang in there! Wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.13,0:17:45.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shush! Dude, don't say a thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.22,0:17:48.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Actually--\N--I keep telling you to keep that mouth shut!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.14,0:17:52.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're too harsh on Kumacy.\NYou're beary harsh.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.56,0:17:55.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the trio that includes my bride caused
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.85,0:18:00.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\Nquite the commotion in your courtyard.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.69,0:18:03.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wait a second...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.36,0:18:06.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that I think about \Nit... Hogback, you pig!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.32,0:18:10.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This means you've raised your\Nhand against my future bride!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.83,0:18:13.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I warned you not to touch her!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.16,0:18:14.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll never get married.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.87,0:18:17.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say what?! Cindry!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.84,0:18:21.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, now, Cindry-chan!\NYou're only adding fuel to the fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.51,0:18:25.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And why are you standing in front of me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.22,0:18:27.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You won't get married, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.64,0:18:32.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're killing me! That \Nwas a nasty stray bullet!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.68,0:18:36.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are they going to do with\NLuffy now that they've caught him?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.02,0:18:39.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And what's happened to Sanji and Zoro?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.69,0:18:41.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're in pretty deep doo-doo ourselves!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.86,0:18:46.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But there is no way Luffy's\Ngonna stay in that cage!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.95,0:18:48.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.62,0:18:50.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.73,0:18:54.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good, good! Keep nice and quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.54,0:18:57.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what anyone says,\Nmy mind is made up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.38,0:18:59.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That woman will be my blushing bride!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.92,0:19:01.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You will never get married.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.88,0:19:03.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.88,0:19:08.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, Cindry-chan!\NWhy don't you just ignore Absalom?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.07,0:19:11.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't expect to get married... ever!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.72,0:19:14.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's two stray bullets in a row!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.14,0:19:17.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She said I'll never get married!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.23,0:19:19.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cut it out! Knock it off!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.52,0:19:21.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't stand all your fussing!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.36,0:19:26.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If those pirates got away,\Nyou can deal with it later!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.40,0:19:29.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I had you gather so we could celebrate
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.57,0:19:37.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the commemorative creation \Nof a powerful ally!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.42,0:19:42.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's insane!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.38,0:19:46.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Master, the pirate chewed\Nthrough the cage and is escaping!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.11,0:19:48.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He chewed...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.47,0:19:49.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...through the cage?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.97,0:19:54.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you capture me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.68,0:19:58.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Luffy!\N--Sweet!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.66,0:20:02.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's going to prove dependable!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.07,0:20:04.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't, Absalom! We're indoors.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.65,0:20:07.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll stop him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.15,0:20:10.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't catch me, dummy!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.62,0:20:14.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Negative Hollow!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.95,0:20:16.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those are...!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.45,0:20:20.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ne-ga-tive! Ne-ga-tive! Ne-ga-tive!...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.83,0:20:25.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're multiplying as they dance! Awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.46,0:20:29.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll catch them and keep them as pets!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.22,0:20:33.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fresh Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.51,0:20:38.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shoot! It didn't work.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.06,0:20:42.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was an epic fail.\NI'm such a loser this week.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.44,0:20:45.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can hear the whole world booing me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.90,0:20:51.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! I've got the punk!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.28,0:20:55.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I could be reborn, I'd like to be a clam.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.58,0:20:57.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I suck!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.87,0:21:05.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That won't work on me a second time!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.30,0:21:15.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I could be reborn,\NI'd like to be a sea cucumber...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.76,0:21:21.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ne-ga-tive! Ne-ga-tive! Ne-ga-tive!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.07,0:21:25.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To fall from the King of the\NPirates to a sea cucumber...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.88,0:21:30.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brutal!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.28,0:21:33.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it! Let go of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.28,0:21:36.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hit him with the light!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.20,0:21:38.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.24,0:21:46.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jerk, I'll get you for this!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.02,0:22:12.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is that?! My shadow?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.84,0:22:36.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, don't do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.11,0:22:50.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've obtained 300 million\NBerries' worth of might!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.44,0:22:58.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now I can complete the greatest\NSpecial Zombie in history!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.37,0:23:11.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.17,0:23:15.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the moment of the \Ncentury, Cindry-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.13,0:23:18.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I saw his corpse in the Land of Ice,\Nmy body wouldn't stop trembling.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.34,0:23:19.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cindry-chan, that's my line!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.80,0:23:22.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was so close to the famous giant known\Nas the legendary "Continent Puller."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.47,0:23:23.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's mine, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.60,0:23:24.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the--
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.85,0:23:26.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a far cry from your line!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.85,0:23:28.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.27,0:23:31.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Warrior Known as the 'Devil'!!\NThe Moment of Oars' Revival!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.23,0:23:39.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
